estring is an extension for string definition/manipulation in OCaml.

url: https://forge.ocamlcore.org/projects/estring/

* Requirements:

  estring depends only on the standard library of ocaml.

* Installation:

  To install estring just type:

  $ make PREFIX=<prefix> install

  You call also do:

  $ make all
  $ make PREFIX=<prefix> just-install

  If you want to install files using a different user.

* Using the library

  estring install the following packages:

  - estring.syntax:
      The estring syntax extension.

  - estring.lib:
      The estring runtime library.

  - estring:
      estring.lib + estring.syntax.

* Development:

  The last development version of estring can always be found in the
  darcs repository hosted at darcs.ocamlcore.org:

  $ darcs get http://darcs.ocamlcore.org/repos/estring/estring
